Usage: justifyBudget [-help] <ptn_or_instname> [-outfile <string>] [-summary]
                     [-view <string>] {-pins <string> }

-help                          # Prints out the command usage
<ptn_or_instname>              # instance or partition name (string, required)
-outfile <string>              # output file name (string, optional)
-pins <string>                 # pins to be analaysed, use * for all pins
                               # (string, required)
-summary                       # reportBudget style summary report
                               # (bool, optional)
-view <string>                 # report only for specified view
                               # (string, optional)